<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-449] svg files not rendering correctly in Microsoft Edge Browser</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-449</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For every svg file in the Lustre Manual figures directory, there is the same image in png format except for the HSM diagram figure 26.1. The HSM figure along with the proposed PCC figures both do not render correctly with Microsoft Edge browser. All other figures look fine in Edge. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Why do we have the same images in two formats for the Lustre manual?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
